metadata.description: From the next generation of characters to make Bluewater famous comes the most infamous of them all! Add in some over-active imagination. Mix in some powdered donuts. Sprinkle it with delusional disorder and you get ...Insane Jane! The kookiest action hero of the 21st century. Will Jane save the day? Will Jane destroy the world? Will she remember to take her medication?
metadata.name: Insane Jane: The Avenging Star, Vol. 2
